name: Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_Right1
logic: Fungus1_09[right1] | Fungus1_09[left1] + ((LEFTCLAW | RIGHTCLAW + WINGS | WINGS + $SHADESKIP | $SHRIEKPOGO[before:ROOMSOUL,after:AREASOUL]) + (SIDESLASH | GREATSLASH | CYCLONE | RIGHTDASHSLASH | LEFTDASHSLASH + DASHMASTER + OBSCURESKIPS) | FULLCLAW + RIGHTDASH + $SHRIEKPOGO[before:ROOMSOUL,after:AREASOUL])

name: Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_Left1
logic: Fungus1_09[left1] | Fungus1_09[right1] + (LEFTCLAW + (LEFTSUPERDASH + RIGHTCLAW + (LEFTDASH | WINGS) | WINGS + LEFTDASH) | RIGHTCLAW + LEFTDASH + WINGS + LEFTSUPERDASH + DANGEROUSSKIPS + PRECISEMOVEMENT | LEFTDASH + (RIGHTCLAW + $SHRIEKPOGO[1,1,1,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL] | $SHRIEKPOGO[1,1,1,1,1,1,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL]) | LEFTCLAW + (RIGHTCLAW | DIFFICULTSKIPS) + $SHRIEKPOGO[2,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL,NOSTALL])

name: Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_1
logic: (Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_Left1 + ((RIGHTCLAW | WINGS) + RIGHTSUPERDASH | ENEMYPOGOS + ((RIGHTDASH | WINGS) + RIGHTCLAW) | (RIGHTDASH + WINGS))) | (Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_2 + (LEFTSUPERDASH | (ENEMYPOGOS)))

name: Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_3
logic: (Greenpath_Sheo_Gauntlet-Group_2 + $SHRIEKPOGO[1,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL] + LEFTCLAW + RIGHTDASH) | (Fungus1_09[right1] + (LEFTCLAW + (LEFTSUPERDASH + RIGHTCLAW + (LEFTDASH | WINGS) | WINGS + LEFTDASH) | RIGHTCLAW + LEFTDASH + WINGS + LEFTSUPERDASH + DANGEROUSSKIPS + PRECISEMOVEMENT | LEFTDASH + (RIGHTCLAW + $SHRIEKPOGO[1,1,1,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL] | $SHRIEKPOGO[1,1,1,1,1,1,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL]) | LEFTCLAW + (RIGHTCLAW | DIFFICULTSKIPS) + $SHRIEKPOGO[2,before:AREASOUL,after:AREASOUL,NOSTALL]))
